      "scoring_520504": "Scoring Procedure and Interpretation:Brief WISDM subscale and Scoring procedureAffiliative Attachment= Mean of items 11, 22, 26Automaticity= Mean of items 1, 10, 14, 25Loss of Control= Mean of items 2, 16, 21, 35Cognitive Enhancement= Mean of items 6, 13, 32Craving= Mean of items 4, 17, 23, 29Cue Exposure/Associative Processes= Mean of items 8, 12, 24Social/Environmental Goads= Mean of items 18, 27, 30Taste= Mean of items 5, 15, 20Tolerance= Mean of items 3, 28, 31, 36Weight Control= Mean of items 7, 19, 34Affective Enhancement= Mean of items 9, 33, 37Total Score= Sum of means for the 11 subscalesThe scoring scheme reflects factors identified in the original publications. Factor structure may differ in individual studies."
